   <text:p text:style-name="P1" loext:marker-style-name="T2"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1" loext:marker-style-name="T2"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1" loext:marker-style-name="T2"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1" loext:marker-style-name="T2"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1" loext:marker-style-name="T2"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5" loext:marker-style-name="T4"><text:span text:style-name="T3">PUBLIC SERVICE ANNOUNCEMENT</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6" loext:marker-style-name="T5"><text:span text:style-name="T5">April 6, 2026</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2" loext:marker-style-name="T1"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P7" loext:marker-style-name="T6"><text:span text:style-name="T6">THIS IS TO</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6"> OFFICIALLY INFORM ALL REGISTERED MEMBERS OF THE NATIONAL MUSLIM COUNCIL OF LIBERIA (INCLUDING COUNTY MEMBERSHIPS, ORGANIZATIONS/INSTITUTIONS, AND MOSQUES) THAT THE HOLDING OF THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY FOR THIS YEAR HAS BEEN APPROVED AND IS SCHEDULED TO TAKE PLACE FROM </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T8">APRIL 25–26, 2026</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3" loext:marker-style-name="T6"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P7" loext:marker-style-name="T6"><text:span text:style-name="T6">ACCORDINGLY, ALL REGISTERED MEMBER ORGANIZATIONS/INSTITUTIONS AND MOSQUES ARE HEREBY REQUESTED TO TAKE NOTE AND SUBMIT THE NAMES OF THEIR RESPECTIVE DELEGATES, IN LINE WITH THE PROVISIONS OF THE </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T8">2021 CONSTITUTION</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6"> (THREE DELEGATES PER INSTITUTION), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T8">ON OR BEFORE APRIL 15, 2026</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">. THIS WILL ENABLE SMOOTH PLANNING AND COORDINATION OF THE ASSEMBLY.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3" loext:marker-style-name="T6"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P7" loext:marker-style-name="T6"><text:span text:style-name="T6">MEANWHILE, OFFICIAL COMMUNICATIONS ADDRESSED TO EACH REGISTERED MEMBER ORGANIZATION/INSTITUTION, MOSQUES REGARDING THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY ARE AVAILABLE FOR COLLECTION AT THE SECRETARIAT OF THE NATIONAL MUSLIM COUNCIL OF LIBERIA HEADQUARTERS DURING WORKING HOURS.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3" loext:marker-style-name="T6"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P7" loext:marker-style-name="T6"><text:span text:style-name="T6">ALTERNATIVELY, ORGANIZATIONS/INSTITUTIONS AND MOSQUES THAT MAY NOT BE ABLE TO VISIT THE SECRETARIAT IN PERSON ARE ADVISED TO OFFICIALLY SUBMIT THEIR INSTITUTION’S WHATSAPP CONTACT NUMBER TO FACILITATE THE SHARING OF THE COMMUNICATION.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P4" loext:marker-style-name="T8"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="No_20_Spacing" loext:marker-style-name="T1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T8">ISSUED BY:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6"><text:line-break/>THE SECRETARIAT<text:line-break/>NATIONAL MUSLIM COUNCIL OF LIBERIA</text:span></text:p>
  </office:text>
 </office:body>
</office:document>